Ortholog(s) have adenine deaminase activity and role in adenine catabolic process, hypoxanthine salvage, purine-containing compound salvage
Ortholog(s) have hydrolase activity, acting on ester bonds, triglyceride lipase activity, role in lipid homeostasis and lipid droplet localization
Ortholog(s) have ubiquitin protein ligase binding activity
Ortholog(s) have role in intracellular phosphate ion homeostasis
Has domain(s) with predicted role in deadenylation-independent decapping of nuclear-transcribed mRNA
Ortholog of C. albicans SC5314 : C1_11850W_A, C. dubliniensis CD36 : Cd36_11100, C. parapsilosis CDC317 : CPAR2_203550 and Candida tenuis NRRL Y-1498 : CANTEDRAFT_113695
Ortholog(s) have water channel activity, role in ascospore formation, transmembrane transport, water transport and plasma membrane localization
Has domain(s) with predicted oxidoreductase activity
Has domain(s) with predicted phosphatidylinositol binding activity
Ortholog(s) have lipid binding activity, role in endocytosis, response to heat and eisosome localization
